ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) correct discrepancies between the French and English versions; (2) harmonize the regulations with the enabling statute, the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION ACT; and (3) add clarity to various regulatory provisions.
